{"tid":1179496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【符合引渡】中國新刑法將施行：散布謠言可判7年","createTime":"2019-05-31T06:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T08:25:18.000Z","uid":47714,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b77916f9e429d78f25d53cdebf4a03f6ac9c40c9","tid":1179496,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20151028-dailynews-criminal-law/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20151028-dailynews-criminal-law%2F&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoGmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=7fe83697\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20151028-dailynews-criminal-law/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/4f22277c646843f3ac5f210859681ecc.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/755/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2F4f22277c646843f3ac5f210859681ecc.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F755%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=f268260c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國《刑法修正案（九）》將於11月1日起施行，散布謠言、私藏極端主義圖書等都將入罪。攝 : Kevin Frayer/GETTY<br />\n<br />\n今年8月審議通過的《中華人民共和國刑法修正案（九）》將於11月1日起正式施行。新修訂的《刑法》將一些常見行為，比如在網絡發布假消息、國家考試中找人替考、虐待老幼病殘等首次列入刑事處罰範圍，最高可判處7年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DerivativeWorksHK/posts/2307629662648812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDerivativeWorksHK%2Fposts%2F2307629662648812&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoGmXZNcgDpxFdooqAHDEnJE%3D&h=28c3a40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DerivativeWorksHK/posts/2307629662648812</a><br />\n<br />\n可判7年，符合李家超同舔共派今日講嘅修訂後之條件（7年或以上嘅罪行就可以引渡番大陸），坐得洗頭艇啦！"},{"pid":"a617fb34de58e166d368ebf3ccd2eec95aea417f","tid":1179496,"uid":220779,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T07:11:13.000Z","msg":"doubke criminality原則<br />\n由於香港散佈謠言唔係刑事罪行<br />\n所以中國唔可以用散佈謠言作罪名要求<br />\n類似嘅咩顛覆國家政權罪同理"},{"pid":"71a320